              <span class="text-2xl mr-3">ğŸ’¬</span>
              <div>
                <strong>WhatsApp/Slack:</strong> Link preview with this image
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <a
            href="/"
            class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-garden-green text-cycladic-white rounded-full hover:bg-garden-green-dark transition-all hover:shadow-lg font-semibold"
          >
            Back to Home
